{"pageid":81515,"pagename":"The Golem/Quick guide","title":"The Golem/Quick guide","displaytitle":"The Golem/Quick guide","revid":14286190,"redirects":["The golem/quick guide"],"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"notoc","value":""},{"name":"description","value":"Quest complete!"}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile navigation-not-searchable rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on The Golem/Quick guide.\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:The Golem/Quick guide\">rsw:The Golem/Quick guide</a></span></div>\n<table class=\"messagebox\">\n<tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 50px;\"><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><img alt=\"Instruction manual.png\" src=\"/images/Instruction_manual.png?13f14\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></div></div></td>\n<td><span class=\"messagebox-title\"><b>This quick guide has an <a href=\"/w/The_Golem\" title=\"The Golem\">in-depth guide here</a>.</b></span><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><div style=\"font-size:0.85em; line-height:1.4em;\" class=\"messagebox-text\">It contains a more detailed description of dialogue, cutscenes, and storyline.\n</div></td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Details\">Details</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Details\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"questdetails plainlinks\" cellspacing=\"3\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Start point</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\"><img alt=\"Quest point icon.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Quest_point_icon.png/17px-Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" srcset=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /> Talk to the <a href=\"/w/Clay_golem\" title=\"Clay golem\">clay golem</a> in the ruins of <a href=\"/w/Uzer\" title=\"Uzer\">Uzer</a>, east of the <a href=\"/w/Shantay_Pass\" title=\"Shantay Pass\">Shantay Pass</a> in the <a href=\"/w/Kharidian_Desert\" title=\"Kharidian Desert\">Kharidian Desert</a>.</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official difficulty</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Intermediate</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Description</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Deep in the desert stand the ruins of the once great city of Uzer, where a lone survivor, an ancient clay golem, forever paces back and forth. It is badly damaged, and its mind cannot rest until it has completed the task for which it was created.\nIt is up to you to uncover the secret of the lost city, and add the final chapter to a story started in the violence of the Third Age.</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Official length</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">Short</td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Requirements</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-input qc-active\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Crafting\" data-level=\"20\"><a href=\"/w/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\"><img alt=\"Crafting\" src=\"/images/thumb/Crafting_icon.png/21px-Crafting_icon.png?a1f71\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"19\" srcset=\"/images/Crafting_icon.png?a1f71 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"24\" data-file-height=\"22\" /></a> 20 <a href=\"/w/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a></span> <sup>(<span title=\"This requirement is boostable\" style=\"cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\">boostable</span>)</sup></li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Thieving\" data-level=\"25\"><a href=\"/w/Thieving\" title=\"Thieving\"><img alt=\"Thieving\" src=\"/images/thumb/Thieving_icon.png/21px-Thieving_icon.png?973fe\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" srcset=\"/images/Thieving_icon.png?973fe 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"25\" /></a> 25 <a href=\"/w/Thieving\" title=\"Thieving\">Thieving</a></span> <sup>(<span title=\"This requirement is boostable\" style=\"cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\">boostable</span>)</sup></li></ul></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Items required</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist no-toggle-parent\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Vial\" title=\"Vial\">Vial</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Pestle_and_mortar\" title=\"Pestle and mortar\">Pestle and mortar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Papyrus\" title=\"Papyrus\">Papyrus</a> (can be bought from <a href=\"/w/Ali_Morrisane\" title=\"Ali Morrisane\">Ali Morrisane</a> for 10gp)</li>\n<li>4 <a href=\"/w/Soft_clay\" title=\"Soft clay\">soft clay</a> (or a <a href=\"/w/Bracelet_of_clay\" title=\"Bracelet of clay\">bracelet of clay</a> and a <a href=\"/w/Pickaxe\" title=\"Pickaxe\">pickaxe</a> to mine northwest of the ruins)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Phoenix_feather\" title=\"Phoenix feather\">Phoenix feather</a> (can be obtained northwest of the ruins)</li>\n<li>Means to enter the desert (such as the <a href=\"/w/Shantay_pass_(item)\" title=\"Shantay pass (item)\">Shantay pass</a>, <a href=\"/w/Desert_amulet_2\" title=\"Desert amulet 2\">Desert amulet 2</a>, <a href=\"/w/Teleport_tablets\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Teleport tablets\">Teleport tablets</a> or <a href=\"/w/Teleport_scrolls\" title=\"Teleport scrolls\">scrolls</a>, <a href=\"/w/Fairy_rings\" title=\"Fairy rings\">Fairy rings</a> or the <a href=\"/w/Pharaoh%27s_sceptre\" title=\"Pharaoh&#39;s sceptre\">Pharaoh's sceptre</a>)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Recommended</th><td class=\"questdetails-info qc-active\">\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist no-toggle-parent\">\n<ul><li>Protective clothing for the <a href=\"/w/Desert_heat\" title=\"Desert heat\">desert heat</a> (<a href=\"/w/Desert_boots\" title=\"Desert boots\">Desert boots</a>, <a href=\"/w/Desert_robe\" title=\"Desert robe\">Desert robe</a>, <a href=\"/w/Desert_shirt\" title=\"Desert shirt\">Desert shirt</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Waterskin\" title=\"Waterskin\">Waterskins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Stamina_potion\" title=\"Stamina potion\">Stamina</a> or <a href=\"/w/Energy_potion\" title=\"Energy potion\">energy potions</a></li>\n<li>Fast travel to <a href=\"/w/Uzer\" title=\"Uzer\">Uzer</a> (<a href=\"/w/Necklace_of_passage\" title=\"Necklace of passage\">Necklace of passage</a> to Eagles' Eyrie or Fairy ring to <span class=\"fairycode\"><b>d</b><b>l</b><b>q</b></span>)</li>\n<li>Fast travel to the <a href=\"/w/Digsite\" title=\"Digsite\">Digsite</a> (<a href=\"/w/Digsite_pendant\" title=\"Digsite pendant\">Digsite pendant</a>, <a href=\"/w/Digsite_teleport\" title=\"Digsite teleport\">Digsite teleport</a> or the <a href=\"/w/Gnome_glider\" title=\"Gnome glider\">Gnome glider</a>)</li>\n<li>Fast travel to the <a href=\"/w/Varrock_Museum\" title=\"Varrock Museum\">Varrock Museum</a> (<a href=\"/w/Varrock_teleport\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Varrock teleport\">Varrock teleport</a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Hammer\" title=\"Hammer\">Hammer</a> and <a href=\"/w/Chisel\" title=\"Chisel\">chisel</a> to remove gems from the throne</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class=\"questdetails-header\">Enemies to defeat</th><td class=\"questdetails-info\">\nNone</td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"hidden\" style=\"display:none\">&#123;&#34;requirements&#34;:&#34;* &#60;span class&#61;\\&#34;scp\\&#34; data-skill&#61;\\&#34;Crafting\\&#34; data-level&#61;\\&#34;20\\&#34;&#62;&#91;&#91;File:Crafting icon.png|21x21px|link&#61;Crafting|alt&#61;Crafting&#93;&#93; 20 &#91;&#91;Crafting&#93;&#93;&#60;/span&#62; &#60;sup&#62;(&#60;span title&#61;\\&#34;This requirement is boostable\\&#34; style&#61;\\&#34;cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\\&#34;&#62;boostable&#60;/span&#62;)&#60;/sup&#62;\\n* &#60;span class&#61;\\&#34;scp\\&#34; data-skill&#61;\\&#34;Thieving\\&#34; data-level&#61;\\&#34;25\\&#34;&#62;&#91;&#91;File:Thieving icon.png|21x21px|link&#61;Thieving|alt&#61;Thieving&#93;&#93; 25 &#91;&#91;Thieving&#93;&#93;&#60;/span&#62; &#60;sup&#62;(&#60;span title&#61;\\&#34;This requirement is boostable\\&#34; style&#61;\\&#34;cursor:help; text-decoration: underline dotted;\\&#34;&#62;boostable&#60;/span&#62;)&#60;/sup&#62;&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;Deep in the desert stand the ruins of the once great city of Uzer, where a lone survivor, an ancient clay golem, forever paces back and forth. It is badly damaged, and its mind cannot rest until it has completed the task for which it was created.\\n\\nIt is up to you to uncover the secret of the lost city, and add the final chapter to a story started in the violence of the Third Age.&#34;,&#34;difficulty&#34;:&#34;Intermediate&#34;,&#34;kills&#34;:&#34;None&#34;,&#34;name&#34;:&#34;The Golem/Quick guide&#34;,&#34;start&#34;:&#34;Talk to the &#91;&#91;clay golem&#93;&#93; in the ruins of &#91;&#91;Uzer&#93;&#93;, east of the &#91;&#91;Shantay Pass&#93;&#93; in the &#91;&#91;Kharidian Desert&#93;&#93;.&#34;,&#34;length&#34;:&#34;Short&#34;,&#34;items&#34;:&#34;* &#91;&#91;Vial&#93;&#93;\\n* &#91;&#91;Pestle and mortar&#93;&#93;\\n* &#91;&#91;Papyrus&#93;&#93; (can be bought from &#91;&#91;Ali Morrisane&#93;&#93; for 10gp)\\n* 4 &#91;&#91;soft clay&#93;&#93; (or a &#91;&#91;bracelet of clay&#93;&#93; and a &#91;&#91;pickaxe&#93;&#93; to mine northwest of the ruins)\\n* &#91;&#91;Phoenix feather&#93;&#93; (can be obtained northwest of the ruins)\\n* Means to enter the desert (such as the &#91;&#91;Shantay pass (item)|Shantay pass&#93;&#93;, &#91;&#91;Desert amulet 2&#93;&#93;, &#91;&#91;Teleport tablets&#93;&#93; or &#91;&#91;Teleport scrolls|scrolls&#93;&#93;, &#91;&#91;Fairy rings&#93;&#93; or the &#91;&#91;Pharaoh&#39;s sceptre&#93;&#93;)&#34;&#125;</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Walkthrough\">Walkthrough</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Walkthrough\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Starting_the_quest\">Starting the quest</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Starting the quest\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Starting the quest\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Travel to <a href=\"/w/Uzer\" title=\"Uzer\">Uzer</a> in the far east of the <a href=\"/w/Kharidian_Desert\" title=\"Kharidian Desert\">Kharidian Desert</a> (north-east of fairy ring <span class=\"fairycode\"><b>D</b><b>L</b><b>Q</b></span>).</li>\n<li>Pick up and read the <a href=\"/w/Letter_(The_Golem)\" title=\"Letter (The Golem)\">Letter</a> west of the broken <a href=\"/w/Clay_golem\" title=\"Clay golem\">clay golem</a></li>\n<li>Talk to the golem. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"Shall I try to repair you?\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-79d303aff3d15b1a9183a4643a2c7141\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-79d303aff3d15b1a9183a4643a2c7141\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>Shall I try to repair you?</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li>\n<li>Use four <a href=\"/w/Soft_clay\" title=\"Soft clay\">soft clay</a> on the golem. If you chose to bring a pickaxe and a <a href=\"/w/Bracelet_of_clay\" title=\"Bracelet of clay\">bracelet of clay</a>, <a href=\"/w/Clay_rock\" title=\"Clay rock\">clay rocks</a> can be found to the north-west, near the shore. The phoenix can be found there as well.\n<ul><li><b>Optional</b>: Mine 5 clay for easy <a href=\"/w/Desert_diary\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Desert diary\">Desert diary</a>, and steal the <a href=\"/w/Desert_Phoenix\" title=\"Desert Phoenix\">Desert Phoenix</a>'s <a href=\"/w/Phoenix_feather\" title=\"Phoenix feather\">feather</a> while nearby.</li></ul></li>\n<li>Talk to the golem again. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"How do I open the portal?\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-b68d4050f31c52b1bdb6baf5fc253af6\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-b68d4050f31c52b1bdb6baf5fc253af6\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>How do I open the portal?</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_statuette\">The statuette</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: The statuette\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: The statuette\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Pick a <a href=\"/w/Black_mushroom\" title=\"Black mushroom\">black mushroom</a> near the stairs east of the golem before heading down (or downstairs at your right).\n<ul><li>Use the <a href=\"/w/Black_mushroom\" title=\"Black mushroom\">black mushroom</a> on the pestle and mortar to get <a href=\"/w/Black_dye\" title=\"Black dye\">black dye</a>. You can do this later if you don't have your <a href=\"/w/Pestle_and_mortar\" title=\"Pestle and mortar\">pestle and mortar</a>.</li>\n<li><b>Note:</b> Take an extra black mushroom if you plan on completing <a href=\"/w/Shadow_of_the_Storm\" title=\"Shadow of the Storm\">Shadow of the Storm</a> soon afterwards.</li></ul></li>\n<li>Climb down the stairs in the ruins.</li>\n<li>Take the <a href=\"/w/Strange_implement\" title=\"Strange implement\">strange implement</a> from the north-western room.\n<ul><li><b>Note:</b> Keep the strange implement if you plan on completing <a href=\"/w/Shadow_of_the_Storm\" title=\"Shadow of the Storm\">Shadow of the Storm</a> soon afterwards.</li></ul></li>\n<li>Head to the most north-eastern part of the <a href=\"/w/Digsite\" title=\"Digsite\">Digsite</a>, near the large buried skeleton, and talk to <a href=\"/w/Elissa\" title=\"Elissa\">Elissa</a>. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"I found a letter in the desert with your name on.\">3</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-6200e6e0c3917500ef03a75e144c6104\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-6200e6e0c3917500ef03a75e144c6104\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>3</b></td><td>I found a letter in the desert with your name on.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div> (make sure to read the letter if no 3rd option is seen)</li>\n<li>Head to the <a href=\"/w/Exam_Centre\" title=\"Exam Centre\">Exam Centre</a> just south of the Digsite.</li>\n<li>Search the bookcase in the south-east corner and read <a href=\"/w/Varmen%27s_notes\" title=\"Varmen&#39;s notes\">Varmen's notes</a>.\n<ul><li>Note: If you have not repaired the golem up to this point, or read Varmen's Notes the curator will not speak to you about the quest.</li></ul></li>\n<li>Talk to <a href=\"/w/Curator_Haig_Halen\" title=\"Curator Haig Halen\">Curator Haig Halen</a> in the <a href=\"/w/Varrock_Museum\" title=\"Varrock Museum\">Varrock Museum</a> about the <a href=\"/w/Statuette_(The_Golem)\" title=\"Statuette (The Golem)\">statuette</a>. <span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"I&#39;m looking for a statuette recovered from the city of Uzer.\">3</span>&#8226;<span class=\"chat-options-underline\" title=\"I want to open a portal to the lair of an elder-demon.\">1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-39538d51ed2405db4aaeabe1cec3daff\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-39538d51ed2405db4aaeabe1cec3daff\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>3</b></td><td>I'm looking for a statuette recovered from the city of Uzer.</td></tr><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td>I want to open a portal to the lair of an elder-demon.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div> (<span class=\"chat-options\">(<i title=\"Chat options\"><img alt=\"Chat\" src=\"/images/Quick_chat_button.png?cf91b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"13\" height=\"10\" data-file-width=\"13\" data-file-height=\"10\" /></i> <span>4</span>&#8226;<span>1</span>)</span><span class=\"hidden js-tooltip-click\" data-tooltip-name=\"c_option-40cb560b09fa4566796c7a5f195e47f6\" style=\"display:none;color:grey;background:none;border:none\"><b>&#8230;</b></span><div class=\"hidden js-tooltip-wrapper\" data-tooltip-limit-width=\"yes\" data-tooltip-arrow-size=\"10\" data-tooltip-for=\"c_option-40cb560b09fa4566796c7a5f195e47f6\" data-tooltip-arrow=\"yes\" style=\"display:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"js-tooltip-text\"><table><tbody><tr><td><b>4</b></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><b>1</b></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div> if <a href=\"/w/Bone_Voyage\" title=\"Bone Voyage\">Bone Voyage</a> is started)</li>\n<li>Pickpocket him for the <a href=\"/w/Display_cabinet_key\" title=\"Display cabinet key\">display cabinet key</a>.</li>\n<li>Head upstairs, and open the second-most western case in the northern-most row. You will get a <a href=\"/w/Statuette_(The_Golem)\" title=\"Statuette (The Golem)\">statuette</a>.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_portal\">The portal</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?section=5&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: The portal\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: The portal\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Return to the <a href=\"/w/Kharidian_Desert\" title=\"Kharidian Desert\">Kharidian Desert</a> (fairy ring <span class=\"fairycode\"><b>D</b><b>L</b><b>Q</b></span>), or teleport to <a href=\"/w/Eagle%27s_Eyrie\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Eagle&#39;s Eyrie\">Eagle's Eyrie</a> with <a href=\"/w/Necklace_of_passage\" title=\"Necklace of passage\">Necklace of passage</a>.</li>\n<li>If you still need the <a href=\"/w/Phoenix_feather\" title=\"Phoenix feather\">Phoenix feather</a>, run north to the clay rocks east of River Elid and pickpocket it from the <a href=\"/w/Desert_Phoenix\" title=\"Desert Phoenix\">Phoenix</a>.</li>\n<li>Return to the ruins of <a href=\"/w/Uzer\" title=\"Uzer\">Uzer</a> where you started the quest and again go down the stairs.</li>\n<li>In the centre of the room will be four alcoves. Place the statuette in the empty one.</li>\n<li>Turn the statues until they all point north.</li>\n<li>Go north, through the double doors.</li>\n<li><b>Optional:</b> Use your chisel and hammer on the throne for 2 sapphires, emeralds, and rubies.</li>\n<li>Otherwise, immediately go back through the south portal.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_golem\">The golem</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?section=6&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: The golem\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: The golem\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"lighttable checklist\">\n<ul><li>Go back upstairs and talk to the golem.</li>\n<li>With an <a href=\"/w/Vial\" title=\"Vial\">empty vial</a> in your inventory, grind the black mushroom using a <a href=\"/w/Pestle_and_mortar\" title=\"Pestle and mortar\">Pestle and mortar</a>.</li>\n<li>Use the <a href=\"/w/Phoenix_feather\" title=\"Phoenix feather\">phoenix feather</a> on the <a href=\"/w/Black_dye\" title=\"Black dye\">black dye</a> to make a <a href=\"/w/Phoenix_quill_pen\" title=\"Phoenix quill pen\">phoenix quill pen</a>.</li>\n<li>Talk to the golem</li>\n<li>Use the <a href=\"/w/Phoenix_quill_pen\" title=\"Phoenix quill pen\">phoenix quill pen</a> on a piece of <a href=\"/w/Papyrus\" title=\"Papyrus\">papyrus</a> to get the <a href=\"/w/Golem_program\" title=\"Golem program\">golem program</a>.</li>\n<li>Use the strange implement on the golem then quickly use the newly acquired golem program on the golem.</li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><b>Quest complete!</b>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Rewards\">Rewards</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?section=7&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Rewards\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/w/File:The_Golem_reward_scroll.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"The Golem reward scroll.png\" src=\"/images/The_Golem_reward_scroll.png?c55f0\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"488\" height=\"320\" data-file-width=\"488\" data-file-height=\"320\" /></a></div></div>\n<ul><li>1 <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\"><img alt=\"Quest points\" src=\"/images/Quest_point_icon.png?dc356\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"21\" /></a>  <a href=\"/w/Quest_points\" title=\"Quest points\">Quest point</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Thieving\" data-level=\"1,000\"><a href=\"/w/Thieving\" title=\"Thieving\"><img alt=\"Thieving\" src=\"/images/thumb/Thieving_icon.png/21px-Thieving_icon.png?973fe\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"21\" srcset=\"/images/Thieving_icon.png?973fe 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"25\" /></a> 1,000 </span> <a href=\"/w/Thieving\" title=\"Thieving\">Thieving</a> experience</li>\n<li><span class=\"scp\" data-skill=\"Crafting\" data-level=\"1,000\"><a href=\"/w/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\"><img alt=\"Crafting\" src=\"/images/thumb/Crafting_icon.png/21px-Crafting_icon.png?a1f71\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"19\" srcset=\"/images/Crafting_icon.png?a1f71 1.5x\" data-file-width=\"24\" data-file-height=\"22\" /></a> 1,000 </span> <a href=\"/w/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a> experience</li>\n<li>2 cut <a href=\"/w/Ruby\" title=\"Ruby\">rubies</a>, <a href=\"/w/Emerald\" title=\"Emerald\">emeralds</a>, and <a href=\"/w/Sapphire\" title=\"Sapphire\">sapphires</a> (collect these by using a <a href=\"/w/Chisel\" title=\"Chisel\">chisel</a> and <a href=\"/w/Hammer\" title=\"Hammer\">hammer</a> on the throne)</li>\n<li>Unlock the carpet ride from <a href=\"/w/Shantay_Pass\" title=\"Shantay Pass\">Shantay Pass</a> to <a href=\"/w/Uzer\" title=\"Uzer\">Uzer</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Required_for_completing\">Required for completing</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?section=8&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Required for completing\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem/Quick_guide?action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Required for completing\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Shadow_of_the_Storm\" title=\"Shadow of the Storm\">Shadow of the Storm</a></li></ul>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"The Golem\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:The_Golem\" title=\"Template:The Golem\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:The_Golem\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:The_Golem?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/The_Golem\" title=\"The Golem\">The Golem</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">NPCs</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Clay_golem\" title=\"Clay golem\"><img alt=\"Clay golem chathead.png: Chat head image of Clay golem\" src=\"/images/thumb/Clay_golem_chathead.png/47px-Clay_golem_chathead.png?bb73c\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"47\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Clay_golem_cha