ht=\"29\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Letter_(The_Golem)\" title=\"Letter (The Golem)\">Letter</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Varmen%27s_notes\" title=\"Varmen&#39;s notes\"><img alt=\"Varmen&#39;s notes.png\" src=\"/images/Varmen%27s_notes.png?33cf7\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"30\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Varmen%27s_notes\" title=\"Varmen&#39;s notes\">Varmen's notes</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Strange_implement\" title=\"Strange implement\"><img alt=\"Strange implement.png\" src=\"/images/Strange_implement.png?27f35\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"30\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Strange_implement\" title=\"Strange implement\">Strange implement</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Display_cabinet_key\" title=\"Display cabinet key\"><img alt=\"Display cabinet key.png\" src=\"/images/Display_cabinet_key.png?2c9d4\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"28\" height=\"27\" data-file-width=\"28\" data-file-height=\"27\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Display_cabinet_key\" title=\"Display cabinet key\">Display cabinet key</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Statuette_(The_Golem)\" title=\"Statuette (The Golem)\"><img alt=\"Statuette (The Golem).png\" src=\"/images/Statuette_%28The_Golem%29.png?3203e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"17\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"17\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Statuette_(The_Golem)\" title=\"Statuette (The Golem)\">Statuette</a><sup>(<a href=\"/w/Statuette_in_alcove\" title=\"Statuette in alcove\">Scenery</a>)</sup></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Golem_program\" title=\"Golem program\"><img alt=\"Golem program.png\" src=\"/images/Golem_program.png?3d117\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"19\" data-file-width=\"25\" data-file-height=\"19\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Golem_program\" title=\"Golem program\">Golem program</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Phoenix_feather\" title=\"Phoenix feather\"><img alt=\"Phoenix feather.png\" src=\"/images/Phoenix_feather.png?b225e\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"31\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"31\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Phoenix_feather\" title=\"Phoenix feather\">Phoenix feather</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Black_mushroom\" title=\"Black mushroom\"><img alt=\"Black mushroom.png\" src=\"/images/Black_mushroom.png?db3d9\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"15\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"15\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Black_mushroom\" title=\"Black mushroom\">Black mushroom</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Black_dye\" title=\"Black dye\"><img alt=\"Black dye.png\" src=\"/images/Black_dye.png?0a33f\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"21\" height=\"30\" data-file-width=\"21\" data-file-height=\"30\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Black_dye\" title=\"Black dye\">Black dye</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Phoenix_quill_pen\" title=\"Phoenix quill pen\"><img alt=\"Phoenix quill pen.png\" src=\"/images/Phoenix_quill_pen.png?3a750\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"31\" height=\"29\" data-file-width=\"31\" data-file-height=\"29\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Phoenix_quill_pen\" title=\"Phoenix quill pen\">Phoenix quill pen</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Locations</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Uzer\" title=\"Uzer\">Uzer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Varrock_Museum\" title=\"Varrock Museum\">Varrock Museum</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Music</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/The_Golem_(music_track)\" title=\"The Golem (music track)\">The Golem</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Forgotten\" title=\"Forgotten\">Forgotten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Throne_of_the_Demon\" title=\"Throne of the Demon\">Throne of the Demon</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Related</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Quick Guide</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Transcript:The_Golem\" title=\"Transcript:The Golem\">Transcript</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐7bfb498f95‐lgkzc\nCached time: 20220517162946\nCache expiry: 3600\nReduced expiry: true\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.185 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.256 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 543/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 35957/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 8167/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.020/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1550977/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  189.128      1 -total\n 44.99%   85.087      1 Template:Quest_details_page\n 16.29%   30.808      1 Template:Quest_rewards_page\n 14.77%   27.941      4 Template:Checklist\n 10.89%   20.598      1 Template:The_Golem\n  9.05%   17.111      1 Template:External\n  8.48%   16.032      1 Template:Navbox\n  7.82%   14.792      5 Template:Chat_option\n  4.34%    8.213      5 Template:Ctg\n  3.54%    6.687      1 Template:Quick_Guide\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:81515-0!canonical and timestamp 20220517162946 and revision id 14286190. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{External|rs}}\n{{Quick Guide}}\n\n==Details==\n{{Quest details page|The Golem}}\n\n==Walkthrough==\n===Starting the quest===\n{{Checklist|\n*Travel to [[Uzer]] in the far east of the [[Kharidian Desert]] (north-east of fairy ring {{Fairycode|DLQ, or necklace of passage to Eagle's Eyrie and collect a phoenix feather}}).\n*Pick up and read the [[Letter (The Golem)|Letter]] west of the broken [[clay golem]]\n*Talk to the golem. {{Chat option|1Shall I try to repair you?}}\n*Use four [[soft clay]] on the golem. If you chose to bring a pickaxe and a [[bracelet of clay]], [[clay rock]]s can be found to the north-west, near the shore. The phoenix can be found there as well. \n**'''Optional''': Mine 5 clay for easy [[Desert diary]], and steal the [[Desert Phoenix]]'s [[phoenix feather|feather]] while nearby.\n*Talk to the golem again. {{Chat option|1How do I open the portal?}}\n}}\n\n===The statuette===\n{{Checklist|*Pick a [[black mushroom]] near the stairs east of the golem before heading down (or downstairs at your right).\n** Use the [[black mushroom]] on the pestle and mortar to get [[black dye]]. You can do this later if you don't have your [[pestle and mortar]].\n**'''Note:''' Take an extra black mushroom if you plan on completing [[Shadow of the Storm]] soon afterwards.\n*Climb down the stairs in the ruins.\n*Take the [[strange implement]] from the north-western room. \n**'''Note:''' Keep the strange implement if you plan on completing [[Shadow of the Storm]] soon afterwards.\n*Head to the most north-eastern part of the [[Digsite]], near the large buried skeleton, and talk to [[Elissa]]. {{Chat option|3I found a letter in the desert with your name on.}} (make sure to read the letter if no 3rd option is seen)\n*Head to the [[Exam Centre]] just south of the Digsite.\n*Search the bookcase in the south-east corner and read [[Varmen's notes]].\n**Note: If you have not repaired the golem up to this point, or read Varmen's Notes the curator will not speak to you about the quest.\n*Talk to [[Curator Haig Halen]] in the [[Varrock Museum]] about the [[Statuette (The Golem)|statuette]]. {{Chat option|3I'm looking for a statuette recovered from the city of Uzer.|1I want to open a portal to the lair of an elder-demon.}} ({{Chat option|4|1}} if [[Bone Voyage]] is started)\n*Pickpocket him for the [[display cabinet key]].\n*Head upstairs, and open the second-most western case in the northern-most row. You will get a [[Statuette (The Golem)|statuette]].\n}}\n\n===The portal===\n{{Checklist|\n*Return to the [[Kharidian Desert]] (fairy ring {{Fairycode|DLQ}}), or teleport to [[Eagle's Eyrie]] with [[Necklace of passage]].\n*If you still need the [[Phoenix feather]], run north to the clay rocks east of River Elid and pickpocket it from the [[Desert Phoenix|Phoenix]].\n*Return to the ruins of [[Uzer]] where you started the quest and again go down the stairs.\n*In the centre of the room will be four alcoves. Place the statuette in the empty one.\n*Turn the statues until they all point north.\n*Go north, through the double doors.\n*'''Optional:''' Use your chisel and hammer on the throne for 2 sapphires, emeralds, and rubies.\n*Otherwise, immediately go back through the south portal.\n}}\n\n===The golem===\n{{Checklist|\n*Go back upstairs and talk to the golem.\n*With an [[vial|empty vial]] in your inventory, grind the black mushroom using a [[Pestle and mortar]].\n*Use the [[phoenix feather]] on the [[black dye]] to make a [[phoenix quill pen]].\n*Talk to the golem\n*Use the [[phoenix quill pen]] on a piece of [[papyrus]] to get the [[golem program]].\n*Use the strange implement on the golem then quickly use the newly acquired golem program on the golem.}}\n'''Quest complete!'''\n\n==Rewards==\n{{Quest rewards page|The Golem}}\n\n==Required for completing==\n\n*[[Shadow of the Storm]]\n\n{{The Golem}}"}